trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the endpoints for a service.
trans-unit.target: En samling som inneholder endepunkt for en tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: This collection of endpoints for a service is used by the metadata API to manage services with multiple endpoints.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen av endepunkt for en tjeneste brukes til å administrere tjenester med flere endepunkt etter metadata API.

trans-unit.source: ServiceEndpointCollection is returned, for example, by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Endpoints%2A> property and by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter.ImportAllEndpoints%2A> method when creating service endpoints from WSDL port types.
trans-unit.target: ServiceEndpointCollection returneres, for eksempel ved den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Endpoints%2A>egenskapen og ved den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter.ImportAllEndpoints%2A>metoden når du oppretter tjenesten endepunkt fra WSDL porttyper.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlImporter.ImportAllEndpoints%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceDescription.Endpoints%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection provides the functionality to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.Find%2A> the endpoints of a particular type, that have a specific name or address, or to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.FindAll%2A> of the endpoints for a service that meet a specified contract type or name criteria.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen inneholder funksjonaliteten for å <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.Find%2A>endepunkt for en bestemt type, som har et bestemt navn eller adresse, eller til <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.FindAll%2A>for endepunkt for en tjeneste som oppfyller kriteriene for typen eller navnet på en angitt kontrakten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.FindAll%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpointCollection.Find%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the first service endpoint found that satisfies the specified contract type from the collection of service endpoints.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer første serviceendepunktet finnes som oppfyller den angitte kontrakten inn fra samlingen av tjenesten endepunkt.

trans-unit.source: This Find overload is specific to the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming model.
trans-unit.target: Denne Finn overlasten er spesifikk for de [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming modellen.

trans-unit.source: It looks at the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A> property for each endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Det ser på den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A>egenskapen for hvert endepunkt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A> may be `null` if the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> was not created from the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming model (types with *Contract attributes).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A>kan være `null` hvis den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription>ble ikke opprettet fra den [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programming modellen (datatyper med * kontrakt attributter).</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.ContractType%2A>
